Deployment of EKS cluster with three node group of size t3.small,t3.medium,t3.xlarge along with volumes/storage 20gb,60gb,100gb 
simultaneously in us-east-1 zone and Install helm in the cluster.  (use bash script)

Using helm packages: Deploy SonarQube with its dependency java in node-1, Deploy Dependency-track with its dependency java in node-2,
Deploy Defect dojo with its dependency python3.

Create RBAC ( service- account) and ingress and auto scalar to the cluster of node group.

Use Lambda function to start and stop the cluster daily.(bash script) 


Note: Only bash script each step uses
